The best model that simultaneously delivers industry-standard accuracy, production line speed, and runs perfectly without a costly GPU is EfficientAD.1. Why it meets Industry Standard AccuracyOn the industry benchmark MVTec AD dataset, EfficientAD achieves an outstanding 99.1% to 99.5% Image AUROC score, making it functionally identical in accuracy to PatchCore. However, unlike typical anomaly detection networks that get confused by complex scenes, EfficientAD incorporates a uniquely structured Patch Description Network (PDN). This network uses strict receptive fields ensuring that fine-grained local pixels map directly to accurate defect regions, allowing it to easily spot micro-defects or larger "logical" structure anomalies (like a missing component)
